{"tid":1259336,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[平台未定]《軌跡》系列新作29日公開！雜誌封面大圖現粉毛女主！","createTime":"2019-06-26T14:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T23:47:21.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0b38ffe6c82fc756fcc5ef23336da7cf72ed19","tid":1259336,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367485990188575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2367485990188575&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=ab25a285\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367485990188575</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Zayazp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Zayazp.jpg&h=91d2bbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《軌跡》系列新作29日公開！雜誌封面大圖現粉毛女主<br />\n<br />\n  電擊PS雜誌官方披露了最新期第677期的雜誌封面大圖和內容介紹，而封面正是經典RPG《軌跡》系列15週年紀念新作的宣傳圖。<br />\n<br />\n  根據報導，軌跡系列新作將會在6月29日的直播節目中正式披露，目前透露出的部分信息包括：<br />\n<br />\n1、作為系列最新作，又是15週年作品，本作會講述以往作品中沒有提及的故事，而不單單是填原來的坑。<br />\n<br />\n2、雜誌封面標題&ldquo;Play&rdquo;底下背對的二人組為本作主角，女主粉色雙馬尾短裙過膝襪，海中還抱著應該是熊的玩偶。<br />\n<br />\n3、麗夏丶諾爾德的青年和斯卡雷特被確認將會登場。<br />\n<br />\n4、新的與舊的VII組成員也有可能登場。<br />\n<br />\n5、可能會涉及到那由多。<br />\n-----<br />\nFalcom《軌跡》RPG新作細節曝光 將展示大陸全貌<br />\n<br />\n  Falcom的近藤社長在新一期《Fami通》透露了關於《軌跡》RPG新作的細節，目前詳細內容還沒有公開，ryokutya2089帶來了一些簡要的爆料，爆料內容比較零散，整理如下。<br />\n<br />\n  他表示《軌跡》新作將會以系列之前作品留下的東西、《閃之軌跡4》中揭示的謎題為基礎構築整體。新公開塞姆利亞大陸全貌（到現在為止走過的帝國還不到大陸全境的一半）。<br />\n<br />\n－主人公似乎是神秘的男女二人。<br />\n<br />\n－瓦吉的服飾不是騎士團裝束。<br />\n<br />\n－庫洛與新角色會走的比較近。<br />\n<br />\n－目前已經明確會登場的角色有麗夏、諾爾德的青年、斯卡雷特。<br />\n<br />\n－可能會和那由多有關。<br />\n<br />\n－平台未定。<br />\n<br />\n－類型是RPG。<br />\n  <br />\n  今年3月時，近藤社長曾公佈了《軌跡》系列新作的幾張人設圖。官方此前表示新作會在今年推出。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePG13UR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePG13UR.png&h=28ca69e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jx8cq8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjx8cq8c.png&h=9f2bdd6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2f85e06962e88bb637c9337547c436c162f29b5","tid":1259336,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a205746d528ce7a8ce3ee8ed1784e48cb2f376","tid":1259336,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T21:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f19c3f666cecf46967a1c0e9639174287a0da0","tid":1259336,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a0d5b665b9376fc6667c2c60dcffbb63c3e3c8","tid":1259336,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801e3fdfbd8b7c1903ff93df95879f3a963d6dfa","tid":1259336,"uid":83442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ebe04d305f6951851a6ae071dd6a4f5dca3293","tid":1259336,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T20:47:51.000Z","msg":"又呃錢<br />\n呢次出幾多集"},{"pid":"f9cd94328f5d8fbbe94898ef5cba0b5476429dbc","tid":1259336,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T21:39:53.000Z","msg":"1、作為系列最新作，又是15週年作品，本作會講述以往作品中沒有提及的故事，而不單單是填原來的坑。<br />\n<br />\n寫多啲嘢<br />\n又整多啲坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p